diset connection instance orcl
diset tpcc tpcc_user test2
diset tpcc tpcc_pass test2
vuset logtotemp 1
vuset unique 1
diset tpcc ora_driver timed
diset tpcc rampup 2
diset tpcc duration 7

buildschema

wait_to_complete

